channel.title: My ip?
channel.description: A few months ago i could launch my servers and register it on server status page.People could play on it. But when i changed my internet (from telenet to belgacom) i couldn't register it anymore and im not sure what my ip is!?!? I checked everwhere on ipchecker... on my command prompt but nothing seems to show my real ip adress! Anyone any suggestions where i could find my real one? or is there other problem??
